Requirements: python, and a unix machine.

11/10/2008

sync.py is a script designed to replicate two already similar directories.

11/10/2008

this script is in the process of being optimized. As of right now it is slower than removing a large directory and copying it.

11/11/2008

added some conditional statements, this increased the speed by a ridiculous amount. Definitely quicker than removing a large directory and copying it.